Package: slimrmodels
Title: Population Genomics Simulations Using SLiM
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Russell", "Dinnage", , "r.dinnage@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "YOUR-ORCID-ID"))
Description: Provides a set of pre-coded population genetics models, written using
  the {slimr} package, which interfaces with standalone software SLiM. These are user-
  friendly functions designed to make running the simulations with different parameters
  easy, and requiring little coding knowledge. Contibutions from the community to this
  package is encouraged.
